reviewText:
2.5D deathmatch between small spaceships that has no reason to exist.
Sort of crappy 2-dimensional Descent where you dig your own tunnels and play vs bots. Boring and repetitive.
3D graphics are very basic(it uses Unity3D engine) Controls are laggy. No online multiplayer and good luck finding someone to play this in split-screen.
This was an impulse buy which I already regret.

reviewText:
This game is fun, but can get boring after awhile. Its a fun game to just to let the time pass. The price is Decent for this game. So I suggest you buy it and try it! :3

One of the negatives in this game is that it doesn't have Online Multiplayer, if it did, I would play it 24/7 and recommend it to my friends. Now it DOES HAVE SPLITSCREEN Multiplayer, but thats it.

I say buy it, hopefully the owners/makers of the game will add Online Multiplayer in the future, but for now I'll give it a 7/10
